item.title: Hands on R
item.description: The purpose of this blog is to document all cool stuff I do in my job. The data used on this blog is data I have collected from my World of Tanks game play. (Disclaimer: I am not the best. Not the worst either!) I am going to put chunks of the data I am using for you to see how the data looks like everytime I am showcasing something new.
